text: The Dishonored Medal is a 1914 silent American adventure film, directed by Christy Cabanne. It stars Miriam Cooper, George Gebhard, and Raoul Walsh, and was released on May 3, 1914. ==Cast list== * Miriam Cooper as Zora * George Gebhard as Lieutenant Dubois * Raoul Walsh as Adopted Son * Frank Bennett as Bel Kahn, son of Achmed * Mabel Van Buren as Anitra * Dark Cloud as Sheik Achmed ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:Films directed by Christy Cabanne Category:American silent feature films Category:American films Category:American black-and-white films
title: The Dishonored Medal
